trans-unit.source: Provides functionality for a stack of client channel sinks that must be invoked during an asynchronous message response decoding.
trans-unit.target: Omfatter funksjonalitet i en bunke klienten kanal mottakere som må aktiveres under dekoding av en asynkron melding svar.

trans-unit.source: The IClientChannelSinkStack is used during processing of responses to asynchronous calls.
trans-unit.target: IClientChannelSinkStack brukes under behandling av svar på asynkrone kall.

trans-unit.source: During a synchronous call, the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method is called when a message is outbound to the server.
trans-unit.target: Under et synkron kall den <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden kalles når en melding er utgående til serveren.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Each sink in the sink chain calls the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A> method on the next sink until the call reaches the transport sink at the end of the chain.
trans-unit.target: Hver sink i sink kjede kall av <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A>-metoden på neste mottakeren til kallet når transport mottakeren på slutten av kjeden.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.ProcessMessage%2A>

trans-unit.source: From there the message is transported to the server.

When the formatter sink is called through the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMessageSink.AsyncProcessMessage%2A> method, it dispatches the call asynchronously by calling <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A> on the next channel sink.
trans-unit.target: Når formatering sink kalles via den <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMessageSink.AsyncProcessMessage%2A>metoden, den sender kallet asynkront ved å kalle <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A>på neste kanal mottakeren.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A> </xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Messaging.IMessageSink.AsyncProcessMessage%2A>

trans-unit.source: A stack of reply sinks is needed to process the response.
trans-unit.target: En bunke svar mottakere kreves for å behandle svaret.

trans-unit.source: Any sink that wants to process the response needs to push itself to the client channel sink stack inside of <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Sink som ønsker å behandle svaret må push selve til klienten kanal sink bunken inne i <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A>.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: Pops the information associated with all the sinks from the sink stack up to and including the specified sink.
trans-unit.target: Viser informasjon som er forbundet med alle mottakere fra sink stakken opptil og inkludert angitte mottakeren.

trans-unit.source: The sink to remove and return from the sink stack.
trans-unit.target: Mottakeren til å fjerne og returnere fra sink stakken.

trans-unit.source: Information generated on the request side and associated with the specified sink.
trans-unit.target: Informasjon generert på side forespørselen og knyttet til den angitte sink.

trans-unit.source: The immediate caller does not have infrastructure permission.
trans-unit.target: Umiddelbar oppkalleren har ikke tillatelse for infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: Pushes the specified sink and information associated with it onto the sink stack.
trans-unit.target: Pusher angitte mottakeren og informasjon som er knyttet til den inn i sink-stakken.

trans-unit.source: The information generated on the request side and specified in the `state` parameter is returned in the `state` parameter of the <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessResponse%2A> method on the corresponding sink.
trans-unit.target: Informasjonen generert på side forespørselen og angitt i den `state` parameteren returneres i den `state` -parameteren for den <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessResponse%2A>-metoden på den tilsvarende sink.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.IClientChannelSink.AsyncProcessResponse%2A>

trans-unit.source: The sink to push onto the sink stack.
Information generated on the request side that is needed on the response side.
trans-unit.target: Informasjon generert på siden som er nødvendig på svar-siden.

trans-unit.source: The immediate caller does not have infrastructure permission.
trans-unit.target: Umiddelbar oppkalleren har ikke tillatelse for infrastruktur.
